<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">IMHO it does not make any difference which order to read them in. I read the books as I am able to obtain them. Read Postmortem after reading about fi<a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">IMHO it does not make any difference which order to read them in. I read the books as I am able to obtain them. Read Postmortem after reading about five other Scarpetta books. Thoroughly enjoyed the book and it was fun to see how Scarpetta's relationship with Marino develops after knowing where it ends up.<a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
