    <div class="section">
      

<div id="review_14064222" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/14064222" />
    <a title="Christy" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/855396-christy"><img alt="Christy" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1358784070p2/855396.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/14064222?book_show_action=true">Jan 30, 2008</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Christy" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Christy" href="/user/show/855396-christy">Christy</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>



        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer14064222" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer9179670640921551999">If you can handle scary, and can look past gory and profane, Patricia Cornwell&apos;s novels are AMAZING. Aside from good old J.K. and Harper Lee, Cornwell is my favorite author. I&apos;m convinced that all the CSI-esque shows were spawned from her books, and if you like that kind of thing, you&apos;ll LOVE these. Gripping, intense, nightmare-inducing ... plus you might learn some new things.<br/><br/>Start with the older books in the series, her newer works aren&apos;t as good.</span>
  <span id="freeText9179670640921551999" style="display:none">If you can handle scary, and can look past gory and profane, Patricia Cornwell's novels are AMAZING. Aside from good old J.K. and Harper Lee, Cornwell is my favorite author. I'm convinced that all the CSI-esque shows were spawned from her books, and if you like that kind of thing, you'll LOVE these. Gripping, intense, nightmare-inducing ... plus you might learn some new things.<br /><br />Start with the older books in the series, her newer works aren't as good.</span>
  <a data-text-id="9179670640921551999" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

