<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/231604.D_j_Dead"><img alt="Déjà Dead (Temperance Brennan, #1)" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1334157601l/231604._SY160_.jpg" />
